Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  3年2班在學園祭上表演的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「羅密歐與茱麗葉」中的羅密歐決定由秋山澪同學扮演了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小澪是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈過去了啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…總覺得主角由投票決定不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既沒有自薦也沒有推薦的人吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我推薦律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有精神又勇敢  還一直在玩摔跤遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些和羅密歐有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人氣超群到連粉絲團都擁有的澪同學在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對是最適合的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  只有小澪和「羅 mio」相符！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不好笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  有什麼關係  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天我來幫你化妝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塗成這～種紫色的眼影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是魔女嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:03:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就在舞台最前列全部拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好像事不關己似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同學  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉的角色就拜託你了  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽扯到自己後立馬變臉啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能演茱麗葉吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  投票結果就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有很多人適合演茱麗葉吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說…紬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這回是負責劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一戀呢  像公主那麼可愛  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過想演公主嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是羅密歐是小澪啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐是小澪的話  茱麗葉就只有小律來演了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是拍檔吧  去保護她啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有裝傻的話  叫人怎麼吐槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是演相聲嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律和小澪是主角的話  劇本就得大幅修改了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然沒什麼人反對了  接著決定別的角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無視我們啊…  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是服裝…  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡  我自薦  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  讓老師做這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒～關～系  我不會做壞事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在害怕什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…學姐的班級要表演短劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是澪學姐就那樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過律學姐竟然會演茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想笑的話就笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中野！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還笑  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那唯學姐呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我演樹G
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A  B  C  D  E  F…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要這麼多樹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…要站著一動不動  這角色真是太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成什麼樣的短劇呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要檢查台詞  先回教室去了  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等澪冷靜下來我們就過去  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擺平這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想變成小豬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分期待著澪學姐的羅密歐  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想演…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那是主角嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年學園祭的舞台是澪學姐獨佔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～你給她致命一擊幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著要去排練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  其實我…要轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為爸爸工作的關係  我要移居到伊爾庫茨克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪裡  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是父親  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之  就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  我一定會在學園祭之後回來的  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會要怎麼辦  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  由我雙胞胎的妹妹來…  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～真是嚇了我一跳  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被選中去演羅密歐  真是奇怪的夢  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實逃避越來越嚴重了啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家為學園祭的演唱會來開始練習吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  放開我  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮額頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和讓我做站著不動的練習  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班伏里奧  班伏里奧在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:06:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法演？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她說無論如何都演不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角還是…  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可惜  但小澪還要準備演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都演不了的話我會重新考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但難得班裡的同學選你  要不要再稍微努力試試？  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很期待著你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳蒙太古  給我站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就變成古裝劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是和  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不覺得大家是認真選的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待秋山同學的羅密歐  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳  蒙太古  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳  蒙太古 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是蒙太古家的羅密歐嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  再融入一點茱麗葉的心情  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來輪到羅密歐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不喜歡的話哪個都…  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  你還在害羞  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…紬太苛刻了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是小律
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的也…  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會只是想說「停」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像做導演一樣太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  澪的聲音實在是太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音很好聽啦  就讓大家都聽一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那注意一下這點  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  從小律開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到天明…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一直…和你說晚安…的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  接下來還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…這樣早晨就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太肉麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台詞算什麼啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這故事算什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是在裝模作樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼討厭家人的話  離家出走不就行了  你這混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全否定莎士比亞？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學這邊也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像也有點擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…律前輩演茱麗葉確實有些困難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這麼爽快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吐嘈都這麼無力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律平時像女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪則像個男孩子這樣練習怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣或許行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從現在開始禁止小律的男生語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿杯子時得兩手拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  把小拇指豎起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還要把襯衫下擺好好塞到裙子裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  平靜不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有些不自然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪這邊也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的有用嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰的地方熱的難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止羅圈腿！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏中是沒辦法的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子也感覺涼涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我們還是現在去提出不演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律…律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把襯衫塞到裙子裡真窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪也換回來  換回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要開始特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣被當作傻瓜你能接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有所謂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排練戲劇？姐姐你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以別進我房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演什麼角色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰  不准笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔唔唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀…戀人的聲音像白銀般溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:43.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ざます（山手語）：山手區域的婦人間流行的敬語，嘲諷這種\N無所事事的人裝模作樣的語言為「ざあます言葉」）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可成不了名演員誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那律試試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天邊浮現曙光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥的腳像犯人的鎖鏈一樣被繫著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果…果然不適合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台詞沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有說錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台詞雖然是記下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說澪啊  笑的太過火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律演的茱麗葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了一想到就要笑的地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪演的羅密歐還不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視線漂浮不定  無論如何都沒有想和你私奔的感覺啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說澪演茱麗葉的話該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份不安的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐  你為什麼是羅密歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律才是  如果演羅密歐的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茱麗葉  為什麼你是如此的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…羅密歐是那樣的角色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起茱麗葉來說更加合適點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了你  即使是大海深處…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是能行嘛  演技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的茱麗葉說不定很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  趕緊到羅倫斯大人那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很開心  但很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律想像澪扮演的茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪想像著小律所扮演的羅密歐來演的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說澪也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊  微笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無…無論多麼悲傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  昨天不是做得很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時只有律在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  想像只有小律一個人就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有律…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准嗤笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能克服在大家面前害羞就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是這樣說沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  這週日有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給小澪做特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我週日有預定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是熟人開的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  今天就在這邊打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用接待客人來克服在大家面前害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  大家  快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  好合身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐也非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說什麼就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有些緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  尺寸應該都說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說是在成長期也可能會有些不合身的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡難受？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是腰部…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是胸部難受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不習慣的時候可能會有些困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之重要的是迎接客人的心情和笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  很可愛  很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小律也來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的蘋果茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛  很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中野！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  秋山小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…大概是躲到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！她藏在那兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊你啊  這樣就沒法特訓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多服務生反而不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了你才到這裡來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們開張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼律你們就一點都不在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說托某人的福已經完全免疫了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  有人叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  快去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…可以點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？啊  好的…請您稍等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…沒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  麻煩您稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  給我筆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有奶酪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才廚房的大叔給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給小澪用下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  給我筆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這就是筆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓…讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到底還是做不來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一直在添麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那試著把客人們當作親近的人來看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親近的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我要聖代  香草冰淇淋  蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…我看看…你等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要大份的布丁拼盤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個我們這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  有的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多放點布丁不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺有點上火…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那就算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過澪學姐還真是適應不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  澪在別人面前的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝司連練習的一半水平都發揮不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過演唱會的時候不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來的確是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為沒地方躲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  逼急了可能就有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  現在也沒什麼客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山小姐和紬小姐也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～澪就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在特訓  就不用休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  我們去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可這樣也太可憐了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  律你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  唯和紬也快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這杯子好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說店裡的茶具都是從歐洲寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社的茶有些也是從這裡拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好貴！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小律你沒看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來我們每天都把這種高級貨當水喝啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來小澪真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去挺為難的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也被逼得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該到火候了吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！小澪太給力了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿分笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…暈過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  澪  你清醒點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對不住你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒白特訓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後接待客人也很上手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  接待客人已經不是問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來這個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就定著變不回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你這麼辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  現在我就幫你治好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平日的小澪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這樣一來戲劇練習就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接待客人和演技完全是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓的意義完全沒了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過笑容卻是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  試一試的話應該能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個說不好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼澪學姐和律學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說從今天起每天練習時間翻倍的話總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  落幕後就悄然離去！退退退退退…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出…這樣下去沒問題吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有好多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道還有沒有座位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:47.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道那份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.51,0:23:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上不能吃甜食…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾點吃蛋糕都無所謂  因為今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:23:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的一切吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.07,0:24:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚別想睡哦  小貓咪～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.78,0:24:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進


